{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Invariant</strong> is an FPS currently in production by a small team of die-hard fans of classic shooters with a  story to tell. Having worked on titles like Serious Sam and Skywind, we're building a game that blends tight combat mechanics with smart puzzles and a unique  narrative in a chilling tone.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351270/extras/halls.gif?t=1734567032\" />A SCIENTIFIC DISCOVERY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set In the frozen expanse of <strong>Antarctica</strong>, you take control of a scientist summoned to the enigmatic <strong>Nabla Station</strong>, a cutting-edge research facility built to unlock the secrets of a potential <strong>world-saving energy source</strong> buried deep beneath the ice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But upon your arrival, chaos erupts: the station\u2019s AI goes rogue while eerie sounds echo from the tunnels near the massive drill.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351270/extras/tunnel.gif?t=1734567032\" />GRAB WHAT YOU CAN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Confused and surrounded by danger, you must traverse the station\u2019s labyrinth of halls, icy exteriors, and treacherous tunnels. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351270/extras/creature.gif?t=1734567032\" />JUST DON'T GET COLD FEET</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Armed with a mix of <strong>inventive tools and powerful weapons</strong>, you\u2019ll face AI-driven machines, strange creatures, and deranged former colleagues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351270/extras/snowmobile.gif?t=1734567032\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> But survival will require more than firepower - <strong>solving puzzles and outsmarting the station\u2019s corrupted systems</strong> will be crucial to reclaiming control and unraveling the station\u2019s dark, chilling secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your contribution is critical - add Invariant to your wishlist!</strong></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3351270?t=1734567032","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351270/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1734567032","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351270/f2f4087260b88c5b97fc5ec296350fd60919a963/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734567032","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351270/f2f4087260b88c5b97fc5ec296350fd60919a963/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734567032","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Invariant</strong> is an FPS currently in production by a small team of die-hard fans of classic shooters with a  story to tell. Having worked on titles like Serious Sam and Skywind, we're building a game that blends tight combat mechanics with smart puzzles and a unique  narrative in a chilling tone.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351270/extras/halls.gif?t=1734567032\" />A SCIENTIFIC DISCOVERY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set In the frozen expanse of <strong>Antarctica</strong>, you take control of a scientist summoned to the enigmatic <strong>Nabla Station</strong>, a cutting-edge research facility built to unlock the secrets of a potential <strong>world-saving energy source</strong> buried deep beneath the ice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But upon your arrival, chaos erupts: the station\u2019s AI goes rogue while eerie sounds echo from the tunnels near the massive dr